## Content Principles

### Clarity
- Write for general audience (not just ReFi insiders)
- Explain acronyms and jargon
- Use simple, direct language
- Structure information logically

### Action-Oriented
- Include clear calls-to-action
- Make next steps obvious
- Provide concrete ways to engage
- Link to relevant resources

### Authenticity
- Show real team members and events
- Use actual community photos
- Transparent about mission and activities
- Honest about impact and challenges

### Accessibility
- Alt text on all images
- Descriptive link text (not "click here")
- Proper heading hierarchy
- Readable font sizes

